text: is a Japanese singer and model. She is a fourth-generation member and the main vocalist of the Japanese idol girl group Angerme. ==Biography== Moe Kamikokuryo was born on October 24, 1999, in Kumamoto Prefecture, Japan. In November 2015, Kamikokuryo was chosen as the sole fourth-generation member of Angerme. ==Filmography== ===Movies=== *JK Ninja Girls ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:People from Kumamoto Prefecture Category:Japanese singers
